 <com:TContent ID="Content">
<h1>Issue 1196 Test</h1>

<p>Popup must appear directly below (or above) each input, not offset to an unrelated position on the page.</p>

<h2>Default (no positioned parent)</h2>
<div id="plain-wrap">
	<com:TDatePicker ID="picker1" DateFormat="yyyy-MM-dd" Mode="Clickable" />
</div>

<h2>Inside a positioned container</h2>
<div id="positioned-wrap" style="position:relative; margin-top:20px; padding:10px; border:1px solid #ccc;">
	<com:TDatePicker ID="picker2" DateFormat="yyyy-MM-dd" Mode="Clickable" />
</div>

<h2>Button mode with pre-selected date</h2>
<div id="button-wrap" style="position:relative; margin-top:20px;">
	<com:TDatePicker ID="picker3" DateFormat="yyyy-MM-dd" Mode="Button" Date="2005-10-20" />
</div>
 </com:TContent>
